## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/cskyconstantpoolvalue">CSKYConstantPoolValue</a> - <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/csky">CSKY</a> specific constantpool value.

This is used to represent PC-relative displacement between the address of the load instruction and the constant being loaded, i.e. (&amp;GV-(LPIC+8)).

Definition at line 46 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/csky/cskyconstantpoolvalue-h">CSKYConstantPoolValue.h</a>.
